conrule="<genericnotice.ps>,\This information is furnished upon the condition that it will not be released to another nation without specific authority of the \, #CONTENT(discl1),\ of the United States, that it will be used for military purposes only, that individual or corporate rights originating in the information, whether patented or not will be respected, that the recipient will report promptly to the United States, any known or suspected compromise, and that the information...\,</genericnotice.ps>"
append="1"></charsubset>
</att>
